          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-body font-sans leading-relaxed border-t border-hairline pt-4">
            The GPA formula divides total grade points by total credit hours: GPA = Total Grade Points / Total Credit Hours. You calculate grade points by multiplying a course's grade point value by its credit hours.
          </div>
        </details>
      
        <details class="bg-canvas ring-1 ring-inset ring-hairline rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lvl2 group">
